name: Dan Jarvis
body:
Manager and Lead Software Engineer with more than 10 years professional experience.

* 5+ years developing native iOS, Android and BlackBerry apps for target devices of all sizes, using Java, Objective C, Xcode, Eclipse, Ant, Git and Subversion.

* 10+ deployed apps across the App Store, Google Play and App World. My latest app has millions of downloads and a better than 4 star user rating.

* 5+ years developing and supporting millions of users on a Linux messaging and call services platform, using Java, C++, Web Services, Perl, SIP, SOAP/XML, and more.
